sources.description:
In this gripping thriller, a group of surfers set sail to a remote spot off the Australian shore.  With six male surfers stuck on a boat, there's bound to be some friction. When two of the surf crew are replaced with girls one of them uses her sexuality to turn rival against rival.  It’s a battle of wits when one man takes over the boat and dominates the group. 

However, some lives will end when a seductive new surfer uses her sexuality to turn rival against rival. 

Directed by Adam Blaiklock
2010
Starring Ben Oxenbould, Daisy Betts, Sam Lyndon
